===== Program =====

It is important to have installed beforehand in your laptops the VO-tools to be used in the School, namely:

     * [[http://aladin.unistra.fr/java/Aladin4Asterics.jar|ALADIN]] (Download the Aladin4Asterics.jar file and execute it from a terminal using "**java -Xmx2048m -jar Aladin4Asterics.jar**") 
     * [[http://www.star.bris.ac.uk/~mbt/topcat/topcat-full.jar|TOPCAT]] (Download the topcat-full.jar file and execute it from a terminal using "**java -jar topcat-full.jar**")
     * [[http://svo2.cab.inta-csic.es/theory/vosa/|VOSA]] (Web server. You don't need to install anything)
     * [[http://www.star.bris.ac.uk/~mbt/stilts/stilts.jar|STILTS]] (Download the stilts.jar file and execute it from a terminal using "**java -jar stilts.jar**")


===== Program =====

**Day 1. Tuesday 15 November**

   * 09:00 Registration

   * 09:30 - 10:15 Introductory talks
      * 09:30 - 09:35 - Welcome (Ada Nebot)
      * 09:35 - 09:50 - {{:open:wp4:school2:asterics-dadi-school-strasbourg-20161115.pdf|The ASTERICS project}} (Rob van der Meer)
