   * 10:15 - 10:45 Coffee break

   * 10:45 - 12:30 Tutorial #1 (1h45m).
      * Title: {{:open:wp4:school2:cds-tutorial-1.pdf|The CDS tutorial}} 
      * VO-tools: Simbad, Vizier, Aladin
      * Tutor: S. Derriere + J. Sorce (group 1) / C. Bot + F.-X. Pineau (group 2)  

   * 12:30 - 14:00 LUNCH

   * 14:00 - 15:45 Tutorial #2 (1h45m) 
      * Title: {{:open:wp4:school2:browndwarfs-tutorial-2.pdf|Discovery of Brown Dwarfs mining the 2MASS and SDSS databases}} 
